model.name: Graphic Crewneck
model.disambiguatingDescription: This standout crewneck sweater features an eye-catching abstract motif in a jacquard weave. Made from medium-weight merino wool, it has a ribbed collar, cuffs and hem and is signed with a round LV medallion on the front.

additionalProperty.name: detailedDescription
additionalProperty.value:
• 100% Wool
  • Multicolor
  • Regular Fit 
  • Model wears a FR M size
  • Model measurements : chest 36’’ / 92 cm, height 6' 2½’’ / 188.5 cm
  • Made in Italy
